features

    - X (opengl backend)
    - pulseaudio support
    - full on screen controller
    - zsh completions


install

    you'll need waf from the AUR
    build with PKGEXT='.pkg.tar' makepkg -cs
    install with pacman -U joshuarli-mpv-0.29.1-1-x86_64.pkg.tar
